{"tid":149302,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個仆街HR故事","createTime":"2017-03-09T07:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T09:05:56.000Z","uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad25568ca76acc35d1cc8f05a5e916743bcfd7b","tid":149302,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T07:55:59.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n<br />\n我聽過朋友A話佢見工果陣識一個HR同事(職位唔高，負責call人interview)<br />\n<br />\n佢過完第一輪面試，到第二輪表現麻麻<br />\n<br />\n但由於佢識果個HR同事關係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHR上司叫佢打電話俾OFFER另一位面試者，<br />\n<br />\n佢就同上司講聯絡唔到佢(事實上無打俾佢<br />\n<br />\n最終上司就話好啦咁唯有俾OFFER阿A啦，<br />\n<br />\n結果A就入到間公司<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHR真係可以好仆街"},{"pid":"3133b5f96c37bf5b27c4ef7fab1d6c86fe162b99","tid":149302,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T07:56:55.000Z","msg":"仆街HR死全家"},{"pid":"7e2a9c8ace1d62c1e728c6e6de3948d15e743cad","tid":149302,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:06:51.000Z","msg":"個hr話唔幫佢奶唔請"},{"pid":"9fe38d47615ccefe72cfa4aedf915ba909379622","tid":149302,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:05:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個hr話唔幫佢奶唔請</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n願聞其詳?男定女?"}]}